    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Into the Sands is a mystery game set in a desert. As a scrapper, explore the dunes and find interesting treasures. As you explore you may uncover exciting information about the desert. Are the nomads aware of the vast history in the desert?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game involves venturing out into the desert and collecting scrap metal to improve your capabilities. As you explore new dialogue options and avenues to investigate will open up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to the desert shopkeeper to get your first tool. Use it to explore and unearth desert objects:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082410/extras/550293d454ea719b1cf1cc2b3b8c62bf.poster.avif?t=1752531838\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082410/extras/550293d454ea719b1cf1cc2b3b8c62bf.webm?t=1752531838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082410/extras/550293d454ea719b1cf1cc2b3b8c62bf.mp4?t=1752531838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk and inquire with the nomads as you play to get more information and help you progress:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082410/extras/575459b265b1bbc1e2f2e59a9ae6c70e.poster.avif?t=1752531838\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082410/extras/575459b265b1bbc1e2f2e59a9ae6c70e.webm?t=1752531838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082410/extras/575459b265b1bbc1e2f2e59a9ae6c70e.mp4?t=1752531838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a sprawling desert landscape littered with scraps and old machinery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn in scrap you find to get access to more tools and improvements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find antique relics and lore that will help you understand the true nature of the desert.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Where did they come from? How does the town survive? Ultimately, it will be up to you to figure out where the mystery leads.</p>",
